<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.10">
<l>perupperutta kaṇṇālaṅ kaḷceytu pēṇinam millattuḷḷē</l>
<l>iruttuvā ṉeṇṇināmi rukkaviva ḷumoṉ ṟeṇṇukiṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>maruttuvappa tannīṅki ṉāḷeṉṉum vārttai paṭuvataṉmuṉ</l>
<l>oruppaṭut tiṭumi ṉivaḷai yulakaḷan tāṉiṭaikkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While we were preparing to perform a huge marriage ceremony,</l>
<l>thinking to keep her in our home, she thought something [else].</l>
<l>Before [anyone] says that she turned away the treatment,</l>
<l>bring them together, [place] her at the side</l>
<l rend="indent">of he who measured the earth!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
